{"tid":2445972,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"HR 唔該入一入黎 expected salary 重唔重要","createTime":"2021-03-14T05:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T12:30:00.000Z","uid":381270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52f91b2907b70a08f976fe5ac9cdb3dea8a0ad3f","tid":2445972,"uid":381270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"請問一下interview個時個 team manger其實 care 唔 care個 expected salary架<br />\n通常in到尾個HR就開始問個salary, 個manger通常都一副不在乎既樣子係到睇下CV就算.<br />\n其實係咪個 Manager 只係決定請同唔請, 如果請既話個HR就要跟我既要求比返個expected salary我? (assume 我唔係寫高到過哂個 market price)<br />\n<br />\n定係個manager都要負責返佢自己team既salary expense? 如果係咁咁個HR有咩用suppose 條team 個salary expense個HR唔會有say"},{"pid":"1b490a0b25f582fbf40d834b88532b82a4ed6f55","tid":2445972,"uid":54721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"HR不嬲都冇用"},{"pid":"03c4c04fb393636d7d96f207f478cf202770ca35","tid":2445972,"uid":381265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"我希望初入職月薪八萬，試用期後再調整。<br />\n呢個係我連登發送匣"},{"pid":"67a1be17f6dcb01ed34c1b9e2c28b7c30450540b","tid":2445972,"uid":381270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"連登無 HR?"},{"pid":"287024e76c5f8efbb446294d9fcd86779e2d81d9","tid":2445972,"uid":20363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"有用，廢事差太遠盞浪費大家時間"},{"pid":"651de16c67e38c730f7aabc48054fbeee63ae49b","tid":2445972,"uid":115728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"方丈都唔識？<br />\n仲要另外開個po問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}